      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LONE RUSTLER (1) is not generally a safe beginner. Latest effort finished 5th over 330m at this track beaten 6 lengths (18.99) behind Cawbourne Dollar in a Grade 5 on March 4. Suited here and can find winning form. ASTON JOE (2) produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at Dubbo over 400m behind Zippy Zenden (23.88) in a Grade 5. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. ORSON JIMMY (8) produced a moderate effort last time when sixth at Wentworth Park over 520m behind Zipping Kendrick (30.78) in a Mix 3/4. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Has ability and can measure up. PA KETTLE (7) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
